Il prossimo hop 10.61.100.1 è risolto via Route 2
→ doppia ricorsione" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f0f8ff;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;align=left;fontSize=9;spacingLeft=8;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="470" y="630" width="400" height="80" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="rt3" value="&lt;b&gt;Default route&lt;/b&gt;
