posto fisicamente nella LAN1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FCE4EC;strokeColor=#C2185B;strokeWidth=2;align=center;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="750" y="760" width="220" height="80" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="drt1" value="route ricorsiva" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;strokeColor=#1565C0;strokeWidth=1.5;dashed=1;" edge="1" parent="1" source="sn1" target="drt"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="drt2" value="10.61.200.0/24" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;strokeColor=#1565C0;strokeWidth=1.5;dashed=1;" edge="1" parent="1" source="drt" target="sn4"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="nat" value="&lt;b&gt;NAT — virtual server (port forwarding)&lt;/b&gt;  [Configuration › Network › NAT]" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;strokeWidth=2;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="30" y="870" width="700" height="200" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="nata" value="&lt;b&gt;NAT 1-to-1 attivo&lt;/b&gt;
Subnet_nat: source LAN1_SUBNET (10.61.10.0/24) ↔ RFC1918_3 (10.61.0.0/16) — nat-loopback ON" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#d6b656;align=left;fontSize=9;spacingLeft=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="50" y="910" width="660" height="50" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="natb" value="&lt;b&gt;Port forwarding ATTIVI&lt;/b&gt;
• wan1 udp/500   → 203.0.113.5 udp/500   (IKE)
• wan1 udp/4500  → 203.0.113.5 udp/4500 (NAT-T)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#d6b656;align=left;fontSize=9;spacingLeft=10;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="50" y="970" width="320" height="90" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="natc" value="&lt;b&gt;Port forwarding DISATTIVATI&lt;/b&gt;
• 203.0.113.3 → DOMV (.116)
• 203.0.113.4 → EGETRAD (.5)
