Accesso da any → 0/0" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5eef8;strokeColor=#9673a6;align=left;fontSize=9;spacingLeft=8;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1060" y="910" width="280" height="70" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="vpnL3c" value="&lt;b&gt;SSL VPN ssl_vpn_intrawelt&lt;/b&gt;  —  pool client 10.61.230.10-250
Network-extension verso: 10.61.10.0/19, 10.61.20.0/19, 10.61.30.0/19, 10.1.116.0/24" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5eef8;strokeColor=#9673a6;align=left;fontSize=9;spacingLeft=8;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="770" y="990" width="570" height="70" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="legL3" value="&lt;b&gt;Protocolli e servizi Layer 3 in uso&lt;/b&gt;
• IPv4 routing forwarding attivo  • IPv6 abilitato con secure-policy6 separate  • ICMP per diagnostica
• DHCPv4 server su lan1/lan2/dmz/guest  • DNS forwarder verso 1.1.1.1 e 8.8.8.8 (DNS security profile RFC1918)
